  <dashboards>
    <dashboard enable-sort-zone-taborder='true' name='Dashboard 1'>
      <style />
      <size maxheight='768' maxwidth='1366' minheight='768' minwidth='1366' preset-index='0' sizing-mode='fixed' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='4' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='97916' id='18' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98828' x='586' y='1042'>
            <zone h='97916' id='15' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98828' x='586' y='1042'>
              <zone fixed-size='940' h='97916' id='8' is-fixed='true' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='68814' x='586' y='1042'>
                <zone fixed-size='694' h='97916' id='7' is-fixed='true' param='vert' type-v2='layout-flow' w='68814' x='586' y='1042'>
                  <zone forceUpdate='true' h='42058' id='12' type-v2='text' w='68814' x='586' y='1042'>
                    <formatted-text>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Executive Summary: Investment Performance &amp; Attribution Analysis</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Reporting Period:</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> 2024 – 2026</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Portfolio Strategy:</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> Quantitative Multi-Asset Allocation</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>1. Performance Overview</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>During the analyzed period, the portfolio delivered a robust total return, consistently outperforming the </run>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>S&amp;P 500 (SPY)</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> benchmark. The </run>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Sharpe Ratio</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> remains at an optimized level, reflecting superior risk-adjusted returns compared to industry peers such as </run>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>QQQ</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> and </run>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>IVV</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>.</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>2. Brinson-Fachler Attribution (Drivers of Alpha)</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>The attribution analysis reveals that the portfolio’s outperformance is primarily driven by:</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Selection Effect (Stock Picking):</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> Significant Alpha was generated within the </run>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Technology</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> sector. Our quantitative selection model successfully identified high-momentum equities that outperformed their sector averages.</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Allocation Effect (Sector Rotation):</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> Strategic overweighting in high-growth sectors during market rallies contributed positively to the total excess return, effectively offsetting the drag from defensive sector positioning.</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>3. Peer Analysis &amp; Risk Metrics</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Volatility Control:</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> Despite market fluctuations, the portfolio maintained a controlled volatility profile, recovering faster from drawdowns than major tech-heavy benchmarks.</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Beta Sensitivity:</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> The portfolio exhibits a calculated Beta that aligns with a &quot;Growth&quot; tilt, providing necessary market exposure while maintaining a margin of safety through diversified holdings.</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>4. Strategic Outlook</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>The automated integration of </run>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>PostgreSQL</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> data feeds ensures that these insights are updated in real-time. Moving forward, the focus will remain on refining sector-specific factor exposures to sustain the current selection alpha.</run>
                    </formatted-text>
                    <zone-style>
                      <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                      <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                      <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                      <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                    </zone-style>
                  </zone>
